Zardus looks over at Wolfgang as he walks toward the lab where Vamprah was. "We're sending a bot to infiltrate the new city the Maximals have. Wheeljack will disguse her as one of them, and we'll find some stuff out. We also have a few new bots."

He enters the lab, looking at Vamprah. "Hello, Vamprah. Meet Wheeljack," he says, stepping aside and gesturing to the mechanic. "He'll get you set up on this."
